 Several social welfare programmes (Ti Manman Cheri, Aba Grangou, Kore Ledikasyon, Kore 
</p>
<p>ekonomi familyal) for Haitians living below the poverty line have been incorporated into the &#8220;EDE 
P&#200;P&#8221; strategic programme. The programme provides for: cash transfers to women heads of 
household, students, older persons and persons with disabilities; food assistance for the extremely 
poor and for schoolchildren; free education for children and literacy training for adults; and, lastly, 
support for economic revitalization in rural and urban areas. </p>


