 http://www.unhchr.ch/huridocda/huridocda.nsf/(Symbol)/A.RES.48.134.Fr?OpenDocument.  
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>21
 A/HRC/PRST/19/2.  
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>22
